1. *Nekad* je bilo sve tako drugačije. (Once it was so different.)
2. *Nekada* smo bili mnogo srećniji. (We used to be much happier.)
3. Znam da si *nekad* bio srećniji. (I know you were happier once.)
4. *Nekad* smo se često viđali. (We used to see each other often.)
5. *Nekad* se u ovom gradu odvijao život mnogo drugačije. (Life used to be very different in this city once.)